    "citation" : "L.G. Thompson, M.E. Davis, E. Mosley-Thompson, E. Beaudon, S.E. Porter, S. Kutuzov, P-N. Lin, V.N. Mikhalenko, K.R. Mountain. 2017. Impacts of recent warming and the 2015/16 El Nino on tropical Peruvian ice fields. Journal of Geophysical Research: Atmospheres, 122(23), 12688-12701. doi: 10.1002/2017JD026592",
    "type" : "publication",
